No. 694. Euclid Park National Bank of Cleveland, Ohio, et al., Petitioners, v. Union Trust and Deposit Company, Trustee. April 15, 1907. Mr. Charles D. Merrick for petitioners. Mr. B. M. Ambler for respondent.

Petition for a writ of certiorari to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals for the Fourth Circuit denied.
